\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 1948 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to Al-Suyuti \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0633\u0645\u0631\u0629 \u0628\u0646 \u062c\u0646\u062f\u0628 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35874,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/28\/shaytan-surah-al-baqarah\/","url_meta":{"origin":35724,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Shaytan: Satan does not enter with Surat al-Baqarah recited","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 28, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Mas\u2019ud reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cRecite Surat al-Baqarah in your houses, for Satan does not enter a house in which Surat al-Baqarah is recited.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2162 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0647\u0650 \u0628\u0646 \u0645\u0633\u0639\u0648\u062f \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Quran Exegesis \u0627\u0644\u062a\u0641\u0633\u064a\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/quran-exegesis-tafsir\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35428,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/03\/27\/best-worship-recitation\/","url_meta":{"origin":35724,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Tilawah: Best worship is recitation of the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Al-Nu\u2019man ibn Bashir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe best act of worship for my nation is reciting the Quran.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 1865 Grade: Hasan li ghayrihi (fair due to external evidence) according to Al-Safirini \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064f\u0639\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0628\u064e\u0634\u0650\u064a\u0631\u064d \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":26496,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2018\/06\/10\/sahaba-iman-before-quran\/","url_meta":{"origin":35724,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: Companions learn faith before the Quran","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 10, 2018","format":false,"excerpt":"Jundub ibn Abdullah reported: We were with the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, while we were strong young boys. We learned faith before we learned the Quran, then we learned the Quran and it strengthened our faith. Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 61 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":28757,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/05\/07\/istighfar-quran-diseases-and-cures\/","url_meta":{"origin":35724,"position":4},"title":"Qatadah on Istighfar: Quran shows us spiritual diseases, their cures","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 7, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Salam ibn Miskin reported: Qatadah, may Allah have mercy on him, said, \u201cVerily, this Quran tells you about your diseases and your cures. As for your diseases, they are your sins. As for your cures, it is seeking the forgiveness of Allah.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 6643 \u0639\u0646 \u0633\u064e\u0644\u0627\u0645 \u0628\u0652\u0646 \u0645\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0643\u0650\u064a\u0646\u064d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Scholars \u0627\u0644\u0639\u0644\u0645\u0627\u0621","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/scholars-ulema\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":35837,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2021\/04\/27\/ten-verses-at-night\/","url_meta":{"origin":35724,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Quran: Ten verses at night, not among heedless","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 27, 2021","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever recites ten verses in the night will never be recorded among the negligent.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n 2003 Grade: Sahih li ghayrihi (authentic due to external evidence) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a \u0647\u064f\u0631\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0631\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]}],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35724","targetHints":{"allow":["GET"]}}],"collection":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/3712"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=35724"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/35724\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=35724"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=35724"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=35724"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}